        "body": "Thanks [~Naganarasimha] for reminding me YARN-2556. I looked at it. It seems like there are some storage level implementations missing in our v2 branch to adopt that patch. Since we're benchmarking on a WIP project, maybe we'd like to organize the benchmarks in a different way? I'll definitely keep an eye on it when working on this one for v2. ",
